---
title: Articles
description: My writing on Hotwire Native, Ruby on Rails, and being a solopreneur.
layout: simple
layout_title: My writing on Hotwire Native, Ruby on Rails, and being a solopreneur.
layout_description: Get started with my latest article and some of my favorites.
---

{% assign posts = site.posts | where_exp: "post", "post.categories == empty" %}

<div class="flex max-w-3xl flex-col space-y-12">
  {% assign latest = posts.first %}
  {% include post.liquid post=latest badge="new" %}

  {% assign all = posts | concat: site.pages %}
  {% assign favorites = all | where_exp: "item", "item.favorite" %}
  {% assign favorites = favorites | sort: "favorite" %}
  {% for post in favorites %}
    {% include post.liquid post=post badge="favorite" %}
  {% endfor %}
</div>
<div class="max-w-prose">
  {% include newsletter/cta.liquid %}
</div>
<p class="mt-16 text-lg text-gray-600 md:mt-24">And all {{ posts.size }} articles I've ever published, most recent first.</p>
<div class="mt-8 md:border-l md:border-gray-100 md:pl-6 md:mt-16">
  <div class="flex max-w-3xl flex-col space-y-16">
    {% for post in posts %}
      {% include post.liquid post=post date=true %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
